{"tid":498110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"難以至信，咪做大嘥鬼的結果居然係比人罵","createTime":"2017-12-13T13:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T09:03:12.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"77cc30013ddcabce8aa8dfc659276d1131cdb6a6","tid":498110,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"話說呢幾日放緊AL<br />\n咁揀咗間酒店獨自食buffet<br />\n有一轉，我夾咗幾舊咕咾肉<br />\n翻埋位食咗舊好撚辣<br />\n屌 原來係宮保雞丁嚟<br />\n咁我唔食得辣 掉咗又好嘥<br />\n於是我行去夾翻落個盤宮保雞丁度<br />\n有旁人厚多士答嗲 提高音<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">E</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">E</span>E<span style=\"font-size: small;\">E</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">E</span> 咁都得，咁唔衛生嫁<br />\n我已經好有禮貌解釋 呢幾舊未掂過..食得唔好嘥...申報自己唔食得辣<br />\n條友企又係度奀住嘴嘰嘰喳喳....好大怨氣<br />\n唔講啲人仲以為我食咗妳隻豬啊"},{"pid":"cbebe7ef8aefef1a8a4fb8c779698b05c9bb75eb","tid":498110,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:15:14.000Z","msg":"你咁撚樣味搞到成碟都比人倒晒<br />\n<br />\n假腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566dc836bb21fd38d877202131f9f7024fc4c71c","tid":498110,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚唔衞生<br />\n夾撚咗埋位就食撚埋佢啦<br />\n唔食得辣咪塞入屎眼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a4130dd75bf5e9a29cc7f4ee9518182673b003","tid":498110,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"045736be09819806042c3d1d7ad59464e4479581","tid":498110,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁撚樣味搞到成碟都比人倒晒<br />\n<br />\n假腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，有無試過夾餸比人食or人哋夾餸比你？<br />\n個原理係一模一樣的"},{"pid":"3428ed41cf7683b81dabe184fb0c4cf5c070850a","tid":498110,"uid":119378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:26:5